# ğŸ¾ HuskyGotchi Ad Network SDK

**HuskyGotchi Ad Network** is a comprehensive advertising solution developed as a final project. It consists of a cloud-based Python server, a robust Android SDK, and a dynamic Admin Portal for managing campaigns.

---

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

This project demonstrates a full-stack advertising ecosystem:
1.  **Android SDK:** A reusable library (`MyAdSDK`) that developers can integrate to display banner ads.
2.  **Demo App:** An Android application ("HuskyGotchi") showcasing the SDK integration.
3.  **Backend Server:** A Python Flask server deployed on Render.
4.  **Database:** MongoDB Atlas for storing ads and analytics (impressions/clicks).
5.  **Admin Portal:** A web interface to create ads and view real-time performance.

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Android App / Demo] -->|Requests Ad| B(Android SDK)
    B -->|GET /api/get-ad| C{Cloud Server - Render}
    C -->|Query| D[(MongoDB Atlas)]
    D -->|Ad Data| C
    C -->|JSON| B
    B -->|Displays| A
    A -->|User Click| B
    B -->|POST /api/click| C
    E[Admin Portal] -->|Manage Ads| C
